---
title: Cherry & Balsamic-Glazed Chicken & Kumara Mash with Garlicky Veggies
description: Oh, happy days! With a heavenly combination of aromatic veggies tossed around in the pan, creamy kumara mash and a
sticky-sweet cherry glaze enveloping the chicken thigh, this is a modern and delicious union that will be happily
devoured by all.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cherry-balsamic-glazed-chicken-60cbec62.jpg
